ProfilePageContent.experienceItem1.title: CEO at MobilityDrive (2009 - present)
ProfilePageContent.experienceItem1.item1: Developed iOS apps which has been installed on over 15 millions devices and RocketScience app was # 1 in the App Store in December 2007.
ProfilePageContent.experienceItem1.item2: Created other games included RPG TrueMasters.
ProfilePageContent.experienceItem1.item3: Co-author of VisualMadness 360 for Global Retailers, enterprise iPad app that provides supermarkets with a way to direct store layouts and perform visual (photo-based) audits.
ProfilePageContent.experienceItem1.item4: Developed a social photo sharing platform / that transcends language and location through video and photo conversations. Used unique UX, localization, real-time translation, and web services.
ProfilePageContent.experienceItem1.item5: Technologies: iOS, C, C++, Objective-C, Parse.com, OpenGL, REST, Web Services, Cheetah3D
ProfilePageContent.experienceItem2.title: Team Lead at MultiMedia LLC (2004 - 2008)
ProfilePageContent.experienceItem2.item1: Developed technical integrations of Right Media Ad server into the Yahoo! APT platform.
ProfilePageContent.experienceItem2.item2: Led numerous end-to-end APT feature implementations from design, development, and testing to production, deployment and monitoring.
ProfilePageContent.experienceItem2.item3: Developed numerous internal-facing tools and web services for Yahoo! Sales and Engineering and Search Marketing groups.
ProfilePageContent.experienceItem2.item4: Developed several tool prototypes and integrated various group efforts for project Panama.
ProfilePageContent.experienceItem2.item5: Developed the Right Media back-end display advertising server system.
